high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the counter.
Pick up the pan from the back of the counter.
Move a few steps left to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the pan.
Carry the pan and turn around. Go forward and then face the white table on the left.
Place the pan on the table, to the right side in the back.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a pan and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn around and walk ahead, then veer left to the white table.
Place the pan on the table to the right of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed pan on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room.
Pick up the pan that is on the counter to the left of the apple.
Turn left and take one step, then turn right to face the sink.
Place the pan in the sink, turn on the water for a two seconds, then turn off the faucet and pick up the pan.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to face the white table.
Place the pan on the table to the right of the bread.
